  <metadesc>Ultimate-PET Commodore PET extended clone</metadesc>
  <overview><p>	
	The Ultimate PET is a re-incarnation of the Commodore PET computer(s) from the later 1970s.
	It is build on a multiple Eurocard board and has only parts that can still be obtained new in 2021.
	It is re-using various technologies from the <a target="_blank" href="../upet/index.html">Micro-PET</a>,
	the <a target="_blank" href="../csa/index.html">CS/A computer</a>, and others. 
	Currently it is a work-in-progress.
 	</p>
  </overview>
